{"tid":604820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[崛起]當中國人拎南泡製作的紀錄片自慰時，突然發現被陰險的韓國人打臉了","createTime":"2018-03-25T06:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T12:31:03.000Z","uid":109923,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ca5c3299d89e78db5fc545cc4fb644f017dbec4e","tid":604820,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T06:07:41.000Z","msg":"南泡之前製作左一套紀錄片 SUPER CHINA 內容講述中國大國崛起<br />\n<br />\n呢條片係中國網絡社群瘋傳，眾人叫好，紛紛拎黎自慰<br />\n<br />\n當然也不忘嘲諷一下台巴子和港燦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/25/140227_0b3ca819ff3d3af9120930251a54f59c.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F25%2F140227_0b3ca819ff3d3af9120930251a54f59c.PNG&h=a2fde26e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直到他們發現這個驚人的事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/25/140227_dc7d0673cbe98afc2f77228ac55e6773.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F25%2F140227_dc7d0673cbe98afc2f77228ac55e6773.PNG&h=4d03e640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n仲未見到？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/25/140227_6dc5cbe8951564120b7120496ed6110c.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F25%2F140227_6dc5cbe8951564120b7120496ed6110c.PNG&h=b1e93638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n再放大啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/25/140226_a700f866cf3e67cb31eb148a0fdeb293.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F25%2F140226_a700f866cf3e67cb31eb148a0fdeb293.PNG&h=0a200790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一條吹奏中國嘅片居然係台獨片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n論陰險 南泡No.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b63b550837df1ab643969b46ae0e1bedbfa434","tid":604820,"uid":7109,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T06:10:45.000Z","msg":"有西藏咪算俾面"},{"pid":"a377887f656b5a67157b95719ab797e4d1c136b9","tid":604820,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T06:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13398322cec1a8a482820d19302e64062a4899a","tid":604820,"uid":169074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T06:21:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4342495d55de59b7c5d3ea78794e5df8aeef0295","tid":604820,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T06:22:22.000Z","msg":"點解唔係影個地球儀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc3e0046254f087a7b1616f1fa407a3445c7263","tid":604820,"uid":33125,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T06:22:48.000Z","msg":"樓主同班中國西打飛機有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab18fd7975d0f529dca448c84ae65bdf82da05b7","tid":604820,"uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T06:24:58.000Z","msg":"同場加映<br />\n<br />\n[門陣特攻？] 事實證明 學殘體字會令人成為文盲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/604837/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/604837/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"97300fe0b859b1e10e229975744ee8e29f8aaf47","tid":604820,"uid"